Pros-
Design- It has got a very sleek design with great looks and is light weight
Display- Curved screen is very good with vibrant colours and crystal clear display
Battery- It has fast charging with good battery backup. Gets charged in 30-60 mins and lasts a day on regular use
Performance - Performance is good, there is some lag on heavy usage

Cons-
Performance- There is a very slight lag on very heavy usage. Could be better in 12 gb RAM as I am us...

Design- It has got a very sleek design with great looks and is light weight
Display- Curved screen is very good with vibrant colours and crystal clear display

Performance - Performance is good, there is some lag on heavy usage

Cons-
Performance- There is a very slight lag on very heavy usage. Could be better in 12 gb RAM as I am us...
